    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about resting anymore. i mean i try to rest, but i just wake up and it's the same pattern starting all over again. the same mistakes, the same failures. it feels like the loop is built into me. like no matter what i do, the end result is always the same. it's just... predictable. and exhausting.",
